{"id":5076,"date":"2018-10-28T12:03:46","date_gmt":"2018-10-28T12:03:46","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/?post_type=publications&#038;p=5076"},"modified":"2022-05-31T16:29:18","modified_gmt":"2022-05-31T16:29:18","slug":"position-paper-european-commission-proposal-for-the-instrument-for-pre-accession-iii-in-the-2021-2027-multiannual-financial-framework","status":"publish","type":"publications","link":"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/publications\/position-paper-european-commission-proposal-for-the-instrument-for-pre-accession-iii-in-the-2021-2027-multiannual-financial-framework\/","title":{"rendered":"Position Paper: European Commission Proposal for the Instrument for Pre-Accession III in the 2021\u20132027 Multiannual Financial Framework"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"accordion-block_62920c807b567\" class=\"accordion-block\">\n      <p>\n      <a href='#'>\n          Publication Details\t\t\t\t\t<svg version=\"1.1\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" x=\"0\" y=\"0\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 10.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"10.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 10.1\" xml:space=\"preserve\"><path d=\"m1.1 3.1 6.9 7 8-8L13.9 0 8 5.9 2.1 0 0 2.1l1.1 1z\" fill=\"#3c3c3b\"\/><\/svg>      <\/a>\n  <\/p>\n  \n  <div class=\"accordion_block_content\">\n          <p>Author: HHC, Unicef, Lumos, Inclusion Europe, European Disability Forum<br \/>\nDate: October 2018<br \/>\nThemes: Disability, European Union, Inclusion<\/p>\n      <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<p>We welcome the European Commission\u2019s (EC) legislative proposal of 14 June 2018 for a regulation establishing the Instrument for Pre-Accession III (IPA III), notably the strong references to fundamental rights, the European Pillar of Social Rights and the 2030 Sustainable Development Goals Agenda.<br>However, in our considered view, the proposed regulation does not adequately reflect the EC\u2019s commitments to implement the Convention on the Rights of Persons with Disabilities (CRPD), including to foster the transition from institutional to family and community-based care through targeted investments. It also fails to ensure consistency and coherence with the European Union\u2019s (EU) internal and external policies and funding instruments.<br>In this paper we make recommendations to the European Parliament, the Council of the European Union and the European Commission.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-file\"><object class=\"wp-block-file__embed\" data=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2018_Position-Paper-on-the-Instrument-for-Pre-Accession-III_FINAL.pdf\" type=\"application\/pdf\" style=\"width:100%;height:600px\" aria-label=\"Embed of 2018_Position Paper on the Instrument for Pre-Accession III_FINAL.\"><\/object><a id=\"wp-block-file--media-058e1311-dff4-471d-8130-923418f55153\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2018_Position-Paper-on-the-Instrument-for-Pre-Accession-III_FINAL.pdf\">2018_Position Paper on the Instrument for Pre-Accession III_FINAL<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hopeandhomes.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/2018_Position-Paper-on-the-Instrument-for-Pre-Accession-III_FINAL.pdf\" class=\"wp-block-file__button\" download aria-describedby=\"wp-block-file--media-058e1311-dff4-471d-8130-923418f55153\">Download<\/a><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Read our recommendations on the European Commission\u2019s legislative proposal of 14 June 2018 for a regulation establishing the Instrument for Pre-Accession III (IPA III).<\/p>\n","protected":false},"featured_media":5078,"template":"","tags":[18,25,86,40,51,85,80,70,55],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO plugin v19.2 - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>Position Paper: European Commission Proposal for the Instrument for Pre-Accession III in the 2021\u20132027 Multiannual Financial Framework - Hope and Homes<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Read recommendations